# 🚀 DevOps CI/CD Project (Node.js + Docker + Jenkins)

## 📌 Overview
This project demonstrates a complete CI/CD pipeline using Jenkins, Docker, and AWS.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Node.js Application
- Docker
- Jenkins
- AWS EC2

## 🔄 CI/CD Pipeline Flow
1. Code pushed to GitHub
2. Jenkins pulls code
3. Docker image is built
4. Container is deployed

## 🐳 Docker
- Dockerfile used to containerize Node.js app

## ⚙️ Jenkins
- Jenkinsfile automates build and deployment

## 🚀 Deployment
- Application deployed on AWS EC2 instance

